# 🖼️ Picture Rotation Web App

## 📌 Project Overview
The **Picture Rotation Web App** is a simple and interactive web-based project developed using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
This application allows users to rotate an image in different directions such as left or right with the help of buttons.

The project demonstrates basic concepts of **DOM manipulation**, **CSS transforms**, and **user interaction**.

---

## 🚀 Features
- 🔄 Rotate image clockwise (right)
- 🔁 Rotate image counterclockwise (left)
- 🎯 Smooth and responsive rotation effect
- ⚡ Simple and user-friendly interface
- 🖼️ Works with any image

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **HTML** – Structure of the webpage  
- **CSS** – Styling and rotation using transform properties  
- **JavaScript** – Logic for handling rotation events  

